<h1>Above Average -- Rpg Rules</h1>

{{markdown (exec "cat" "rules.md")}}

<h2>Traits</h2>

{{range $k,$c := sort_on "name" (load_cards "cards/skills.crd")}}
<h3>{{$c.name}}{{if has $c.data.params}} ( {{sep " / " (as_list $c.data.params)}} ){{end}}</h3>
